-01-30T11:10:16.000Z","msg":"政府勾地政策 嚴重干預自由市場"},{"pid":"31a06727863a3533f874da606f7226c246f587af","tid":1852271,"uid":205043,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"年宵禁乾貨"},{"pid":"5ac1f56dd033e8af7010580597c3e3221315d68e","tid":1852271,"uid":338630,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"MTR食咗KCR"},{"pid":"26cda0c60ac7d2e6dd3e288e6acce085f66f4cb3","tid":1852271,"uid":49979,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"31a06727863a3533f874da606f7226c246f587af","tid":1852271,"uid":205043,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"年宵禁乾貨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:13:02.000Z","msg":"然後民間搞就用部門左踢右踢<br />\n<br />\n令到紅磡果個最後搞唔成"},{"pid":"7c97bffa934e4e17c8a0d05e8fb41f32cb5a34c9","tid":1852271,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:13:51.000Z","msg":"食米儲備量"},{"pid":"bbe9e0a842f3c19855bca1fcef3b74f73caa6bee","tid":1852271,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:15:02.000Z","msg":"不如講有咩政府<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇</span></span>于預自由市場的行為啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708ad7c9c223cfff53118846f607a892aab76953","tid":1852271,"uid":245033,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:18:22.000Z","msg":"100億資助海洋公園算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b04def8ebf4b8d7c8262a9249f3816ef37d704","tid":1852271,"uid":70264,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:19:58.000Z","msg":"我係自由市場嘅支持者 (我諗係)<br />\n因為我係偏向John Stuart Mill嘅自由論觀點<br />\n政府越管理得市民事務細緻 市民就越無自由<br />\n如果大家想要自由民主 係唔應該由政府出手<br />\n而係民間互相組織解決 <br />\n<br />\n我覺得政府喺今次件事 應該係無咩干預嘅手段可以幫到人<br />\n限制最高價格我認為唔好<br />\n假設市場係無晒貨 而只可以由外地輸入<br />\n如果個價太高 其他國家價錢高啲<br />\n咁就只會廠商先輸入他國<br />\n香港就排隊 等他國市場滿足咗先<br />\n<br />\n一係就政府幫大家採購 然後派<br />\n但其實咁只係財富分配政策 唔係啲咩干預<br />\n即係收咗稅 派錢畀基層 然後畀你買口罩<br />\n但係咁做 即係食呢家嘅炒價 甚至更高<br />\n如果大家覺得呢家係貴到離譜唔抵買 更加唔應該用呢招<br />\n但係從財富分配政策角度睇 可以話係派錢平息怨氣"},{"pid":"835d1aef50032b5cf5454d7f816e4157b29a8ca1","tid":1852271,"uid":156618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:22:24.000Z","msg":"乜都市場話事，而家市場要求換走曬班高官呀，又唔見你仆仆街落台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6715b5d7c2b85a08deb2cff0ac6ec4c2bb853611","tid":1852271,"uid":20690,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:24:55.000Z","msg":"政府係行積極不干預<br />\n佢要話市場有問題就干預<br />\n玩晒"},{"pid":"c08e3766fc023a48e1a763c8b25f0425b0390afa","tid":1852271,"uid":50873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:24:55.000Z","msg":"政府採購口罩供應市場本身已經係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526f313a9d5a89206b82e120f31b38147abd5c5d","tid":1852271,"uid":84102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:26:32.000Z","msg":"HKTV <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩維基頂到"},{"pid":"0d911c72588cf890c2ed64fd4799cfdbd10982ac","tid":1852271,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"藥房咩人開<br />\n自己諗下"},{"pid":"cf2c7b28e5943ae59f4b95fc63ddd0c97cccb88f","tid":1852271,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:27:13.000Z","msg":"加煙稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc7187dfb3247cadbd2a01af545bd3d7b242dc6","tid":1852271,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d5630a1a217b705386ff625e00a0933bc67c9b6","tid":1852271,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:06:09.000Z","msg":"加汽車首次登記稅,其實車太多,塞車太耐,無耐性嘅人就會自然走去坐其他交通工具,就汽車數量同馬路就會回復平衡。<br />\n<br />\n咁政府做咩要干擾佢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:27:19.